Manually installed:
pyfits-3.0.5
libusb
    cd libusb
    ./build.sh
libccd

1) install Mac Port package:
http://www.macports.org/

2) as root
    a) port selfupdate
    b) port install 

3) cd extern/
    as user, configure and build pyfits, libusb
    as root, install pyfits
    as user, install libusb
    as user, install libccd
4) 
    
